      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R1) holds current FDA-recognized V&V documentation and internal version-control audit trail. SQA level 2 requires documented test suite and change-control procedures.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 is covered by the vendor's V&V summary report filed with FDA under the 510(k) predicate pathway. Internal SQA records confirm version-controlled solver builds, regression test suite (>1200 cases), and documented change-control procedures consistent with MRL 2 requirements."
