      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver order-of-accuracy confirmed via method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) benchmark at level 2 for the turbulence and transport equations employed.",
      "rationale": "MMS benchmarks for the SST k-omega turbulence model and scalar transport equations confirm second-order spatial accuracy. Published ANSYS verification reports and in-house Poiseuille flow benchmarks corroborate expected convergence rates, satisfying level 2 numerical code verification."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
