      "rationale": "Three-mesh Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI values between 1.8% and 3.2% for NIH across all five operating points. Prism layer y+ maintained below 5 throughout the impeller passage. Discretization error is bounded and acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
