      "rationale": "Bench experiments conducted at the FDA/CDRH flow laboratory used bovine blood at 37°C ± 0.5°C, hematocrit 33 ± 2%, and flow rates verified by calibrated Coriolis flowmeter (±0.5% FS). All five operating points replicated within stated uncertainty bounds. Test condition documentation meets level 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
