      "rationale": "NIH is the primary validated output and maps directly to the RH acceptance criterion via the ASTM F1841 normalization procedure. The transformation introduces less than 2% additional uncertainty. Relevance of QoI to the COU decision is confirmed at level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
