      "rationale": "The Giersiepen power-law damage accumulation model was selected based on a comprehensive synthesis of prior hemolysis modelling studies (see literature-synthesis-vr), which demonstrates consistent predictive performance across multiple rotary blood pump platforms. SST k-omega turbulence closure is appropriate for the rotating passage flow regime. Model form selection is justified at level 2."
